<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c4">[مُذَأَّب]</span>: غلام مُذَأَّبٌ: له ذؤابة.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>... فُعالة، بضم الفاء<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
